[{"url_token": "wang-xin-yu-79-75", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "78433049", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "78433049", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "沿着海边骑。。。。。。羡慕嫉妒恨呀。。。。。。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "Sherpa", "author_id": "f4f1fbb34394151b9aa8393065981a23", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "wang-xin-yu-79-75", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "78432815", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "78432815", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我骑公路都不敢上50，怕须弥，旅行相对重，不怕须弥，反正你也骑不了那么快，我放坡30就已经危机感重重了，可能我胆小，怕刹不住。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "Sherpa", "author_id": "f4f1fbb34394151b9aa8393065981a23", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "chen-yun-long-24", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "75008831", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "75008831", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "14年7月的时候我也是沿着海边骑，昆山到深圳。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "桃桃乌龙", "author_id": "f19126f0585987a01d229e523e09488d", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "73489648", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "73489648", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "只住店的话，每天完全可以控制在70以下。其次就是你走得这条线城市化程度很高，晚上露营会很吵闹，所以休息不好对长途骑行也是不好的。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "Curl123", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "74439829", "reply_comment_id": "74427651", "reply_root_comment_id": "73489648", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "对了，洗发沐浴牙刷等记得自备，还有毛巾。不管你露营还是住店，最好都自备。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "知乎用户amqh8L", "author_id": "46c05202a47cb29e8da82f09c4d86c3e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "Curl123", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "74439735", "reply_comment_id": "74427651", "reply_root_comment_id": "73489648", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "个人需求不同吧，出行一年了，除了10块钱一个人的没有空调无线以外，都能洗澡（独立卫生间），而且全部都有无线，顶多没空调。入住之前要先看房间再决定是否入住，也要学会避开风俗区。因为我是女的，帐篷诸多不便，洗漱不方便不说，没有Wi-Fi对于更新游记也不太方便，再一个也是担心车子和行李的安全。感觉题主对住宿要求颇高，可能住几天帐篷就哭了。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "知乎用户amqh8L", "author_id": "46c05202a47cb29e8da82f09c4d86c3e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wu-wei-lin-51", "headline": "离我水果摊远点儿", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "74427651", "reply_comment_id": "74400254", "reply_root_comment_id": "73489648", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "这些旅馆的基本配置跟如家相比怎样呢？我觉得长途骑行的话如家这类快捷酒店算是基本需求了，而且其他旅馆，非连锁的可能没能做到标准化配备，比较随便。比如说现在到某个地方，不找如家汉庭七天这类连锁，随便找个住下，虽然便宜了点，住进之后要洗澡才发现没洗发液沐浴露没热水没浴巾，洗完澡躺床上发现被子上有毛发或者一些肮脏东西，而且还没空调没无线。虽说长途旅行不应太挑剔住的，但我觉得这些算是最基本要求吧，说到底干净最重要，这是保证自己有个好睡眠，第二天精力充沛的前提。简单的说我就是想找个能够安心躺下的地方。但同时又得考虑价格，毕竟如家和你们说的那些旅馆价格差了很多，能省下一笔不小的钱做别的事。答主你觉得呢？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "炜林", "author_id": "52cb5a2f966f24a70091e1d66dca76b8", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "Curl123", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "74400254", "reply_comment_id": "73545730", "reply_root_comment_id": "73489648", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "非一线城市，旅店宾馆很少有价格上80一晚的。青旅反而可能更贵。要合理利用团购软件。我们一路下来北方地区30-50一晚，南方多在70左右。大城市也有99连锁旅店，或者团购如家七天，最贵是130左右一晚。更有许多便宜的家庭旅馆可以选择。注：所有宾馆旅店记得砍价。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "知乎用户amqh8L", "author_id": "46c05202a47cb29e8da82f09c4d86c3e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "73546611", "reply_comment_id": "73545730", "reply_root_comment_id": "73489648", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "另：住酒店你问别人就好了，举例福鼎如家，价格是399一晚，仅供参考。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}, {"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "73546523", "reply_comment_id": "73545730", "reply_root_comment_id": "73489648", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我只是住一般的小旅店，我是穷游的，如果每天都是如家，我住不起，而且也不是所有城镇都有快捷酒店。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}, {"url_token": "wu-wei-lin-51", "headline": "离我水果摊远点儿", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "73545730", "reply_comment_id": "73489648", "reply_root_comment_id": "73489648", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "住什么店七十以下？  难道是青旅？青旅就算了吧哈哈。而且我们是两个人的。就算住最便宜的如家一晚也要一百以上。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "炜林", "author_id": "52cb5a2f966f24a70091e1d66dca76b8", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "wu-wei-lin-51", "headline": "离我水果摊远点儿", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "73394590", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "73394590", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "感谢大竹。我还想问一下如果沿途不想住店的话，露营可行否？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "炜林", "author_id": "52cb5a2f966f24a70091e1d66dca76b8", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "wu-wei-lin-51", "headline": "离我水果摊远点儿", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "73481213", "reply_comment_id": "73406821", "reply_root_comment_id": "73394590", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "但是我觉得如果露营不住酒店的话一个月省下的这笔钱也不小了，大概三四千，可以干其他很多事了。所以我一直纠结要不要住酒店", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "炜林", "author_id": "52cb5a2f966f24a70091e1d66dca76b8", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "73406821", "reply_comment_id": "73398435", "reply_root_comment_id": "73394590", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "车子锁外面，东西放进帐篷，丢的风险肯定有，所以尽量选择人少的地方露营。其实我觉得完全没必要住帐篷。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}, {"url_token": "wu-wei-lin-51", "headline": "离我水果摊远点儿", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "73398435", "reply_comment_id": "73395032", "reply_root_comment_id": "73394590", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "自行车以及其他装备不怕丢了吗？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "炜林", "author_id": "52cb5a2f966f24a70091e1d66dca76b8", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "73395032", "reply_comment_id": "73394590", "reply_root_comment_id": "73394590", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "露营也无不可，找无人空旷的地方就可以。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}]}]